description:
​River Raid​ is a classic game made for the atari 2600.
This is a smaller version made in C to run in RIVES​ for the RISC-V retro Jam #1​.

Controls:
- Directionals left and right to move horizontally;
- Up to speed up;
- Down to slow down;
- Z key or gamepad button A1 to fire;

The game sources are available at its GitHub repository.
